parameters: \nc<>This is the magical girl's hideout, isn't it? It's so cute~!

\nc<>Sorry for being noisy. I'm the type of kid who likes this
kind of thing.

\nc<>No, if you're Levantia's sidekick, then you're also my
comrade!
\nc<>I'm happy to be praised for this.

\nc<>...Yeah, the key registration is done. With this, Reina can
come and go freely.
\nc<>So, what do you want to talk about?
\nc<>Ah, I forgot. I heard it, senpai.

\nc<>You started streaming to enhance the power of magical
girls, right?

\nc<>That's right. Magical girls become stronger as they receive
emotions from their listeners.

\nc<>You've found a pretty good place, but there is a fatal
weakness in streaming.
\nc<>Well... it takes time for a channel to grow!

\nc<>They reacted so lightly! It's actually a pretty serious
opinion, you know!?

\nc<>If you're not careful, it can take years to achieve
meaningful results!

\nc<>There's some truth to that. This industry is quite tough,
you know.

\nc<>There's a possibility that you could get buried among the
countless videos if you're not careful.
\nc<>That's right! Blue Sorbet understands it well.

\nc<>It doesn't matter how good the content is, if it doesn't
stand out, it's meaningless.

\nc<>So, in order to become popular right from the start, I
propose collaborating with Matsuo-kun!

\nc<>It's decent. It's not well-known among the general public,
but if you're looking for related videos, it often comes up.

\nc<>My main focus is on health-oriented home training-based
YouTubers, but with my good looks and skilled speaking
ability, I have expanded into various types of content. Now,
I am a veteran YouTuber with over 500,000 subscribers on my
channel.

\nc<>Oh, now that I think about it, I feel like my older brother
was also watching it!

\nc<>Wow, they're famous. But I wonder if someone like that
would collaborate with someone like me who just started
streaming?

\nc<>Hehehe. I won't hide it, but I'm already in talks with
Matsuo-san! You can praise me if you want!
\nc<>Wait, hold on! I'm not mentally prepared yet...

\nc<>You're not going to do it? Well, if that's the case, I
guess there's nothing I can do...
\nc<>You know, new streamers don't last very long, right?

\nc<>(Ugh, it's true... If things continue like this, I might end
up being buried. And if that happens, I won't be able to
help anyone or be helped...)
\nc<>I understand. Let's give it a try.

\nc<>As expected of you, senpai! I thought you would say that,
so I've already decided on the schedule.
\nc<>Reina-san is quick at her work, isn't she?
